# Test Fixtures

This directory contains test fixture files.

## Excel Fixtures

Excel fixtures are generated using `create_fixtures.py`.

### Generating Fixtures

```bash
# From project root
python tests/create_fixtures.py
```

This will create `sample_data.xlsx` with various data types for testing.

## Fixture Files

- `sample_data.xlsx` - Sample Excel with integer, string, float, boolean, and date columns
